**Budget under $4,000 / Maximum size / Lab:**
[2ct IGI F-VVS1 lab emerald cut](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-search?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) in the [Petite Solitaire WG at $1,115](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/petite-four-prong-solitaire-engagement-ring-in-18k-white-gold-item-194979?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational). Total: **$3,344.** Two certified carats of lab diamond in the setting that best serves the shape. Nothing else in the under-$4,000 ring market matches this for certified quality and carat size.

