[2ct IGI D-FL Ideal lab emerald cut](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/28828463?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) in the [Riviera Pavé WG at $1,515](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/riviera-pave-diamond-band-engagement-ring-in-18k-white-gold-item-195326?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational). Total: **$6,250.** Flawless. D colour. Ideal cut. 2ct face-up. Pavé band sparkle. The hall-of-mirrors effect at its purest. This is the best emerald cut ring in the market at this price tier.

